ess of each marketing campaign.  At 200OK solutions, we believe that the if you are trying to hit a particular sales goal, gain more visitors and members then do as we do - create a look and feel which will get your target audience to sit up and take notice, thus promoting your brand identity.</p>\n<p>200OK Solutions stretches SharePoint''s capabilities beyond your firewall for designing a perfect website design for you. We make the best use of the functionalities on offer and make optimum use of SharePoint investments to lower the overall TCO.</p>\n<p>Your feedback for the website design and development strategy is always incorporated in our processes and we progress through the project by affecting multiple revisions in the site. Once the design is approved, we design and develop sites in the SharePoint environment similarly and then carry out the data migration process. We never compromise with our efforts and your vision, ever!</p>\n</div>\n</div>			  </div>    </div>    <div id="bottom-line">	<div id="bottomtxt" class="copyright">Copyright © 2013 200ok Solutions, All Rights Reserved   | <a href="http://www.200oksolutions.com/sitemap.html">Sitemap</a>		<div id="social-icon">                <a target="_top" href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/200-Ok-Solutions/177844325688305"><img src="fb-icon_17.jpg" alt="" style="padding-right: 15px;" height="24" width="24"></a> <a target="_top" href="https://twitter.com/200oksolutions"><img src="twter-icon_19.jpg" alt="" style="padding-right: 15px;" height="24" width="24"></a> <a target="_top" href="https://plus.google.com/113567871805408654471/posts"><img src="gplus-icon.jpg" alt="" style="padding-right: 15px;" height="24" width="23"></a> <a target="_top" href="http://www.linkedin.com/company/2517819?trk=tyah"><img src="linkdin-icon_23.jpg" alt="" height="24" hspace="50" width="24"></a> </div>	</div>\n</div>  </div>\n</div></body>\n</html>\n', 'PAGE=SECTION,L2=HEADER,L81=FOOTER,L44=NAV,L71=ARTICLE,', '', '20140924152636', 'ht