(47, '<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd">\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">\n<title>Website and Forum support for the Big Fish Campaign</title>\n<meta name="DESCRIPTION" content="Website and Forum support for the Big Fish Campaign">\n<meta name="KEYWORDS" content="big, fish, campaign, website, forum, admin, owner, support">\n<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="index.css" media="all">\n<style type="text/css"></style>\n</head>\n<body><div id="wrapper">  <div id="header"><a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/index.html"><img src="bfc-logo.jpg" alt="Big Fish Campaign" border="0" height="150" width="211"></a></div>    <div id="content">	    <div id="content-left">			<p><a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/support.html" class="side">Supporters:</a></p>			<p><a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/retail_support.html" class="side">Retailers</a></p>			<p><a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/wholesaler_support.html" class="side">Wholesalers</a></p>			<p><a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/pfk_support.html" class="side">Practical Fishkeeping</a></p>			<p><a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/public_aquaria.html" class="side">Public Aquaria</a></p>			<p><a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/other_support.html" class="side">Other Supporters</a></p>			<p><a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/website_support.html" class="side">Websites / Forums</a></p>			<p><a href="http://www.facebook.com/BigFishCampaign"><img src="facebook.jpg" alt="Find us on Facebook" border="0" height="40" width="40"></a><a href="http://twitter.com/BigFishCampaign"><img src="twitter.jpg" alt="Follow us on Twitter" border="0" height="41" width="41"></a></p>		</div>	    <div id="top-menu">			<a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/index.html" class="menu">Home</a> / <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/aims.html" class="menu">Aims</a> / <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/news.html" class="menu">News</a> / <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/support.html" class="menu">Support</a> / <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/articles.html" class="menu">Articles</a> / <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/links.html" class="menu">Links</a> / <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/contact.html" class="menu">Contact</a>		</div>    <div id="content-main">	<h1>Website and Forum Support</h1>	<p>Websites and forums can also help to spread the word about the Big Fish Campaign, and help make hobbyists more aware of the problems that can arise if fish are purchased without researching their potential size first.</p>	<p>If you are a website owner/admin, you can help by placing links to bigfishcampaign.org on your pages and forums.</p>	 <table border="0" cellpadding="5"><tbody><tr><td>	   <p>You can also display the Big Fish Campaign logo showing your support:</p>	   <p><img src="backingthebigfishcampaign.jpg" alt="We''re backing the Big Fish Campaign" align="left" border="0" height="200" width="222"></p>	  </td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Websites already supporting the Big Fish Campaign include:</p>	<p><a href="http://www.seriouslyfish.com/">Seriously Fish</a></p>	<p><a href="http://www.thetropicaltank.co.uk/">The Tropical Tank</a></p>	<p><a href="http://injaf.org/">INJAF - It''s Not Just A Fish</a></p>	<p><a href="http://www.ukaps.org/">The UK Aquatic Plant Society</a></p>	<p><a href="http://tropicalfishkeeping.info/">tropicalfishkeeping.info</a></p>	<p><a href="http://www.fishkeeping.co.uk/">fishkeeping.co.uk</a></p>	<p><a href="http://www.theaquaristlist.com/">The Aquarist List</a></p>	<p><a href="http://www.sturgeon-pond.info/blog/the-big-fish-campaign/">Sturgeon Pond Info</a></p>	<p><a href="http://www.africancichlidsireland.com/">African Cichlids Ireland</a></p>	<p><a href="http://neaquaticcommunity.myfreeforum.org/index.php?component=indexpage">North East Aquatic Community</a></p>	<p><a href="http://www.thesaltybox.com/">The Salty Box</a></p>		</div>    <div id="content-right">    	<p><img src="bf_one.jpg" alt="Big Fish need Big Homes!" name="myimg" height="130" width="200"></p>	<p align="center">Big Fish need Big Homes!</p>	<p><img src="bf_two.jpg" alt="Big Fish need Big Homes!" height="130" width="200"></p>		</div>  </div>    <div id="footer">\n<a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/index.html" class="menu">Home</a> - <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/aims.html" class="menu">Aims</a> - <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/news.html" class="menu">News</a> - <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/support.html" class="menu">Support</a> - <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/articles.html" class="menu">Articles</a> - <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/links.html" class="menu">Links</a> - <a href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/contact.html" class="menu">Contact</a>\n</div>    <div id="bottom">Copyright 2012-2014 <a title="Big Fish Campaign" href="http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/" class="side">Big Fish Campaign</a>\n</div>\n</div></body>\n</html>\n', 'PAGE=SECTION,L2=HEADER,L14=NAV,L51=NAV,', '', '20140924153232', 'http://www.bigfishcampaign.org/website_support.html');
